# Cloudflare Pages -- Redirect Rules
# CF Pages NATIVELY handles clean URLs:
#   /page.html  -->  automatically accessible at  /page
#   (and /page.html -> 308 redirect to /page)
#
# WARNING: DO NOT add explicit rewrite rules like:
#       /page  /page.html  200
#     They cause INFINITE redirect loops with CF Pages built-in 308.
#     Wildcard rule "/* /:splat.html 200" is also DANGEROUS -- it intercepts
#     real .html requests and serves the wrong file (often index.html).
#
# Only add rules here for:
#   - 301 permanent redirects (old URL -> new URL)
#   - External redirects (/buy -> https://affiliate.com/...)
#   - SPA fallback (/* /index.html 200) -- only for true SPAs
#
# Example (safe -- actual redirects, not rewrites):
#   /old-page  /new-page  301
#   /go        https://example.com/affiliate  302
